	<fo:inline font-family="monospace">/camí/a/fitxer</fo:inline>.  Per exemple:
	<fo:inline font-family="monospace">/etc/fstab</fo:inline>
      </fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="chap-book-conventions-commands"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pt" font-family="sans-serif,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="sans-serif,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.optimum="1.0em" space-before.maximum="1.2em" text-align="start" start-indent="0pt"><fo:block font-size="17.28pt">Comandaments ?Comandes?</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">
	Els comandaments estàn impresos en negreta. Per exemple: <fo:inline font-weight="bold">ls
	-l</fo:inline>
      </fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="chap-book-conventions-screenoutput"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pt" font-family="sans-serif,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="sans-serif,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.optimum="1.0em" space-before.maximum="1.2em" text-align="start" start-indent="0pt"><fo:block font-size="17.28pt">Eixida per pantalla</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">
	Les eixides per pantalla es veuen així:
      </fo:block><fo:block id="idm967031268" text-align="start" wrap-option="no-wrap" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.maximum="1.2em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1.2em" hyphenate="false" white-space-collapse="false" white-space-treatment="preserve" linefeed-treatment="preserve" font-family="monospace">
Hola Món!
      </fo:block><fo:block space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">
	Si els comandaments s'estàn introduïnt en la pantalla d'eixida,
	s'imprimiràn en negreta:
      </fo:block><fo:block id="idm967030900" text-align="start" wrap-option="no-wrap" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.maximum="1.2em" space-after.minimum="0.8em" space-after.optimum="1em" space-after.maximum="1.2em" hyphenate="false" white-space-collapse="false" white-space-treatment="preserve" linefeed-treatment="preserve" font-family="monospace">
$ <fo:inline font-weight="bold">comandament</fo:inline>
Eixida
      </fo:block><fo:block space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">
	Si s'executa un comandament com a root, l'interpret es mostrarà 
	com <fo:inline>“#”</fo:inline>. Si un comandament s'executa amb un usuari normal
	sense privilegis, l'interpret es mostarà com
	<fo:inline>“$”</fo:inline>.
      </fo:block></fo:block><fo:block id="chap-book-conventions-notes"><fo:block><fo:block><fo:block margin-left="0pt" font-family="sans-serif,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" keep-together.within-column="always"><fo:block keep-with-next.within-column="always"><fo:block font-family="sans-serif,Symbol,ZapfDingbats" font-weight="bold" keep-with-next.within-column="always" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.optimum="1.0em" space-before.maximum="1.2em" text-align="start" start-indent="0pt"><fo:block font-size="17.28pt">Notes</fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block></fo:block><fo:block space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">
